Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.80,0:01:36.90,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,When he steals into a mansion with a friend\nin order to help him win over his love,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.01,0:01:40.00,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...the young man witnesses a physical\nliaison between two adults.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.44,0:01:43.07,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,My friend said to me,\N"He must know."
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.51,0:01:48.07,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,"Until the day his innocent soul\nis destroyed."
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.05,0:02:03.01,count fo,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(350,350)}Act 8:\NA Night in Boulogne
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.75,0:02:24.28,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,This is bad...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.89,0:02:26.08,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Albert!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.99,0:02:28.79,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,W-What are you\nbarging in here for?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.09,0:02:33.22,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry. I kept calling,\nbut you didn't answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.13,0:02:36.50,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You have a visitor from\nthe Champs Elysees.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.73,0:02:38.67,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,The Count?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.90,0:02:42.34,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,His Excellency says that he does\nnot wish to see you today.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.77,0:02:44.24,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Did he give you a message\nor something?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.37,0:02:46.27,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,No, Monsieur, nothing\nin particular.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.01,0:02:47.98,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.88,0:02:49.64,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.75,0:02:52.04,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,His Excellency wishes\nto unveil his new villa.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.15,0:02:55.64,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,That is an invitation to a dinner party.\NBy all means, bring your entire family.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.28,0:02:58.68,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,With pleasure!\NWhere is the villa?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.29,0:03:01.62,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,The forest of Auteuil.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.42,0:03:03.95,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,He has a villa in\nthat gloomy place?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.43,0:03:08.42,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. His Excellency insisted\non this villa in particular.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.71,0:03:30.21,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,If I'm not mistaken, Monsieur Villefort\nused to own this villa.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.15,0:03:32.78,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It's almost fallen\nto ruin.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.29,0:03:37.38,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,While his first wife was still alive,\Nit was a bright, cheerful place.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.89,0:03:41.26,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You mean Valentine's\nreal mother?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.86,0:03:44.73,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,She was still so young and\nbeautiful when she died.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.62,0:04:07.32,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.52,0:04:09.85,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,My lord General.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.99,0:04:11.89,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for\ninviting us.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.40,0:04:19.63,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Count!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.60,0:04:23.16,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Well, well! The good\NMadame Villefort!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.24,0:04:25.80,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,This is my husband, the...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.27,0:04:30.01,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,The Crown Prosecutor,\NI presume?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.55,0:04:34.48,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'm told that you did a great\nservice for my wife and son.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.35,0:04:39.32,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I am honored that you have gone\nto all the trouble of coming here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.79,0:04:44.82,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,This manor is a little too dreary to\Ninvite guests over, don't you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.16,0:04:51.12,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Not at all, I have taken quite\na liking to the silence here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.00,0:04:59.84,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Now, I see that the three gentlemen who\nembody Paris are gathered here tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.58,0:05:02.63,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Monsieur Danglars,\nthe king of bankers.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.18,0:05:05.77,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,General Morcerf, who commands\nthe military.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.88,0:05:08.87,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,And you, Monsieur, who\nadministers the law.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.05,0:05:15.08,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,There is a reason that I invited you here\nto this humble affair tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.12,0:05:18.59,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Allow me to be frank and\nmake a confession to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.53,0:05:24.33,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Travelers are insecure\nby their very nature.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.03,0:05:29.63,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I would like to forge bonds of friendship\nwith you three gentlemen.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.44,0:05:36.64,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I am given to understand that you hope\nto win the presidency, General.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.55,0:05:39.41,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Where did you\nhear that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.81,0:05:43.68,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I would like to assist you to the best\nof my humble abilities.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.15,0:05:47.64,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Albert. Leave us\nfor a moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.79,0:05:49.09,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What? But l...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.69,0:05:52.02,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,We adults need to have\na discussion.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.83,0:05:59.56,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Albert, what's the matter?\NYou look a little out of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.12,0:06:18.61,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You don't look well.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.49,0:06:22.08,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,No, I'm fine, Mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.29,0:06:24.26,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry I forced you\nto come.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.30,0:06:30.99,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if the Count\nis avoiding me...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.17,0:06:35.26,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,At Valentine's house,\NI saw something.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.90,0:06:40.71,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I saw the Count and Madame Villefort\nbeing... intimate.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.44,0:06:42.47,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,So?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.55,0:06:48.45,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,While I was watching,\nthe Count spotted me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.02,0:06:52.42,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It seemed that way\nto me, anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.05,0:06:54.28,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.39,0:06:56.45,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a terrible person...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.39,0:07:02.56,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I guess the Count has\na lot on his plate.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.13,0:07:05.60,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It just means that he's\na man like any other.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.43,0:07:10.34,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, weren't you supposed to go there to\nwork out the whole Maximilien situation?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.94,0:07:13.87,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,That's the least of my\nworries right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.15,0:07:19.14,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.35,0:07:23.34,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Would it be all right\nif I joined you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.65,0:07:24.85,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Who is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.69,0:07:28.21,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going outside for\nsome fresh air.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.32,0:07:29.85,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Um, might l...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.59,0:07:35.46,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell\ndid you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.43,0:07:39.30,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,And who might\nyou be, boy?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.43,0:07:41.87,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,M-Me, sir? I am...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.04,0:07:45.97,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,This is Captain Maximilien Morrel,\na most capable soldier.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.54,0:07:48.51,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,How do you do, sir?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.64,0:07:53.27,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Captain Maximilien Morrel,\NCanes Venatici Gamma Army.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.58,0:07:58.11,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,My family operates a trading\Nfirm in Marseilles. As for me, l...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.22,0:08:00.48,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,And what do you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.79,0:08:03.92,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Sir. I-I would like to ask for\nyour daughter's hand in...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.03,0:08:08.26,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Yours is a noble profession,\none which defends the state.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.70,0:08:10.86,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,For that, I offer you\nmy respects.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.00,0:08:13.76,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Nevertheless, you are\na simple commoner.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.87,0:08:16.27,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,And my daughter\nis already engaged.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.74,0:08:19.57,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I suggest that you bear\nthose facts in mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.81,0:08:23.84,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,How rude!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.91,0:08:28.97,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Bouillabaisse à la Marseilles.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.86,0:08:38.72,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,So, how did the marriage\nproposal go?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.13,0:08:41.69,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Dead on arrival.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.46,0:08:46.20,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You know, maybe she really\nhas feelings for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.30,0:08:48.03,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,And what's this secret\nconversation about?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.17,0:08:50.03,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Beauchamp!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.14,0:08:54.51,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You've got guts, firing off a flash\Nat the Crown Prosecutor like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.68,0:08:58.87,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,When I see a guy who's full of himself,\Nmy rebellious streak takes over.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.21,0:09:01.65,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,So, what's up?\NThe sorrows of youth?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.75,0:09:06.12,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Geez, what a sad world we're living in.\NIt's all "love" this and "affairs" that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.62,0:09:07.65,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Look at that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.89,0:09:11.52,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Rumor has it that those two were\nhaving an affair years ago, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.33,0:09:15.06,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,The Crown Prosecutor\nand Eugenie's mother used to...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.13,0:09:18.57,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Forgive me for imposing\non you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.67,0:09:20.66,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It's all right.\NDon't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.34,0:09:24.97,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I've paid a small fortune\nfor her lessons.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.14,0:09:27.30,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It's only fair that she should put it\Nto good use at times like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.62,0:09:39.45,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Please listen to what\NI have to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.66,0:09:43.65,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'd like to apologize\nto you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.29,0:09:50.89,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What I said the other day was terrible.\NI didn't give any thought to your feelings.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.00,0:09:53.87,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What did Valentine say?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.57,0:09:57.09,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,She was crying.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.91,0:10:04.35,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I guess I made you do my\ndirty work for me. I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.15,0:10:09.11,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Valentine loves you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.22,0:10:10.45,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You're kidding!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.65,0:10:11.91,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,She does!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.42,0:10:15.48,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.89,0:10:21.52,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Eugenie's gotten really good,\nhasn't she?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.63,0:10:23.69,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, don't try to change\nthe subject.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.90,0:10:26.80,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I talked to her\nthe other day.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.20,0:10:29.97,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I bet she had a lot of bad things\nto say about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.24,0:10:31.60,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Pretty much.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.37,0:10:36.00,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What's that mean?\NTell me! C'mon, tell me!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.18,0:10:42.45,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What do you want from me\nafter all this time?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.82,0:10:43.72,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'm frightened.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.82,0:10:45.58,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What if someone\nsees us?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.79,0:10:49.55,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,But when we're here, I can't help\nbut think of our child!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.79,0:11:19.01,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Magnificent.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.85,0:11:22.88,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I see that music is truly\nyour calling.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.42,0:11:28.86,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Her calling, huh? The Count must\nknow a lot of talented people.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.43,0:11:34.09,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for the lovely performance,\nmy lovely lady.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.01,0:11:40.50,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,How do you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.01,0:11:46.95,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Now that one talented youth has made her\ndebut, allow me to introduce another.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.58,0:11:50.78,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,This is Marquis Andrea Cavalcanti.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.15,0:11:54.05,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, my...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.52,0:11:59.19,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,That family had\nan heir?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.56,0:12:02.76,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,His father is an old friend\nof mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.26,0:12:07.29,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,If you would welcome him as you have done\nme, nothing would make me happier.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.07,0:12:11.70,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I realize that I am an untested youth who only\nrecently inherited his late father's estate,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.34,0:12:13.90,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...but I am honored to\nmake your acquaintance.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.01,0:12:17.88,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Look at that brooch!\NIt easily cost five million!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.15,0:12:21.34,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Who's that guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.58,0:12:24.02,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,The Count's new favorite, I'd say.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.99,0:12:27.78,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I bet he has all kinds\nof talents!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.82,0:12:31.95,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Well, ladies\nand gentlemen.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.16,0:12:38.00,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I do hate to interrupt your conversation,\nbut if I might have your attention please?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.03,0:12:41.73,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,One of the reasons that I\npurchased this estate...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.04,0:12:47.70,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...was that I wished to escape from the noise of\nthe city and spend time in quiet contemplation.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.14,0:12:51.77,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,But on the contrary,\nonce I arrived here,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.11,0:12:56.41,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...I found myself fascinated by a certain\naura that pervades this old mansion.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.39,0:13:00.15,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,And what might\nthat be?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.46,0:13:06.12,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,How might one\nbest describe it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.06,0:13:09.85,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Yes... In a word...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.90,0:13:12.24,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...a curse.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.07,0:13:15.50,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I found myself pondering\ncertain questions.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.87,0:13:19.33,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What sorts of lives were led by\nthe people who once lived here?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.87,0:13:24.97,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,And what sad events occured here that\nwere hidden away from the eyes of all?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.18,0:13:33.38,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,When my mind toys with such thoughts, I am\nfilled with inexpressible joy and tranquility.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.99,0:13:39.15,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,No doubt about it...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.59,0:13:41.72,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It's him,\NI'm sure of it...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.06,0:13:45.00,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Preposterous!\NA curse, the very idea...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.93,0:13:49.77,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Monsieur Prosecutor, you suggest\nthat you do not sense...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.87,0:13:52.97,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...the gloomy, malevolent aura\nthat pervades this mansion?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.31,0:13:54.97,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,That's CROWN Prosecutor.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.84,0:13:59.87,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Very well. I take it, then, that you must\Nsee it with your own two eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.62,0:14:06.88,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,In truth, there is one room deep inside\Nthis mansion that has been left exactly as it was.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.32,0:14:09.12,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Why would you do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.43,0:14:15.42,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I am convinced that\nit is that room...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.90,0:14:19.56,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...which is the source of the\nmalevolent aura here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.51,0:14:26.74,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,How rude!\NWe're leaving.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.84,0:14:27.74,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Monsieur!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.01,0:14:31.45,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Now, now, now, don't be\nlike that!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.78,0:14:35.44,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I for one say that we should indulge\nour host's eccentricities.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.62,0:14:42.45,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What do you say, everyone? Why don't we\ngo see this "evil room" for ourselves?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.56,0:14:43.89,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Just a moment, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.43,0:14:48.12,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Going all at once would\nspoil the entertainment.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.30,0:14:49.59,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Monsieur Albert!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.57,0:14:51.40,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.87,0:14:52.83,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Monsieur Franz!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.67,0:14:55.14,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,And Mademoiselle Eugenie.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.77,0:14:56.76,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.34,0:15:01.10,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I suggest that you split into three groups\nto search for the room.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.71,0:15:05.87,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,We shall have these three youths\nlead the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.68,0:15:10.78,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I will offer a small gift to those\nwho successfully reach...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.89,0:15:14.84,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...the innermost depths\nof this dark mansion.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.12,0:15:16.32,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Are we agreed?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.39,0:15:20.16,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I like it!\NThis sounds like fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.50,0:15:22.69,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,By all means,\nlet's do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.23,0:15:26.89,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Monsieur Albert, if you\nwould be so kind?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.44,0:15:31.50,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.21,0:15:39.51,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It's been a long time,\NMarquise.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.92,0:15:42.31,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You're looking well.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.78,0:15:44.48,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Keep your mind\non the task at hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.65,0:15:47.14,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,As they say, it's the early bird\nthat gets the worm.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.82,0:15:50.81,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Incidentally, Marquis Andrea,\nwhere are you from?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.36,0:15:55.19,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Oh. Excuse me. I come from the\nfar reaches of the eastern galaxy.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.66,0:15:58.89,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,There is a beautiful planetary\ncluster there.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.80,0:16:03.24,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,And on one of those planets\ncan be found a bird...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.54,0:16:05.87,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...which eats ore and lays\neggs of jewels.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.34,0:16:09.57,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Once every 50 years, they build a colony\nfor the purpose of mating, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.39,0:16:21.41,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,We can finally speak\nprivately now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.92,0:16:24.15,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Pardon me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.71,0:16:41.16,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Count. I need to say\nsomething to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.31,0:16:46.51,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Whatever is the matter,\NMadame Morcerf?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.92,0:16:50.82,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Please, call me Mercedes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.92,0:16:54.91,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,This heart of the malevolent aura\nthat he mentioned...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.52,0:17:00.76,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What do you suppose\nits heart really is?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.23,0:17:08.93,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you so fixated\non Marseilles?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.84,0:17:11.13,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Whatever do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.41,0:17:15.17,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You served another dish from Marseilles\nfor dinner tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.71,0:17:17.58,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Was it not to your liking?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.68,0:17:23.48,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,No. It's just that when I look at you,\NI am reminded of someone I once knew.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.89,0:17:30.76,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,For many years, I have lived with\nthe desire to see him once again.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.53,0:17:35.72,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,But now, I'm filled with\na terrible foreboding...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.24,0:17:42.53,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Count?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.14,0:17:46.63,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You are not alone. Never.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.88,0:17:51.68,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,There is someone who\nis always thinking of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.58,0:17:55.88,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Please don't forget that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.69,0:18:04.99,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,This is my good luck charm. It was\ngiven to me by my late father.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.63,0:18:08.03,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'd like you\nto have it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.13,0:18:12.43,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It's a dead end...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.83,0:18:17.77,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I've had enough of this, Albert.\NMadame Danglars is tired, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.04,0:18:19.10,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,We're turning back.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.21,0:18:20.43,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Monsieur Villefort!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.14,0:18:22.37,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,There's a door inside!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.31,0:18:25.40,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,T-This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.24,0:18:50.53,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Congratulations to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.47,0:18:54.57,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Your party is the first\nto arrive.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.41,0:19:01.61,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Did you enjoy the unique ambiance\nthat this mansion has to offer?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.28,0:19:06.01,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I see that the master of this house doesn't\nknow the proper way to entertain guests!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.22,0:19:12.62,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Monsieur Albert, might I\nask for your assistance?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.89,0:19:14.33,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.63,0:19:23.04,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for playing along.\NIt must have been difficult.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.61,0:19:26.84,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, Count.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.58,0:19:29.94,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry? Whatever for?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.21,0:19:39.42,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,The truth is, I... I saw you.\NIn Madame Villefort's greenhouse.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.42,0:19:45.45,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Goodness, how awkward.\NYou saw us, did you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.83,0:19:48.95,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Madame would not take no\nfor an answer, you see.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.53,0:19:53.06,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I simply assumed that you\nwere angry with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.87,0:19:55.30,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Perish the thought!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.24,0:20:04.73,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Incidentally, it is I who\nshould apologize to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.08,0:20:08.34,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I have been unable to speak\nwith you properly until today.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.18,0:20:13.64,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,The fact of the matter is that I suffer from\nan illness I contracted in distant space.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.05,0:20:18.99,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,From time to time, I wish to\nrest without seeing anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.23,0:20:26.43,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.20,0:20:31.93,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It is nothing serious. I do feel a\Nnumbness from time to time, however.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.41,0:20:40.01,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Albert. This is a secret\nknown only to you and me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.18,0:20:44.35,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,A secret between\nyou and me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.92,0:20:50.12,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I understand.\NI give you my word.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.99,0:20:54.15,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,In that case, let us carry\nthis box through the door.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.60,0:20:58.19,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,This is the room where\NI gave birth to the child!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.30,0:21:03.33,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,The child... The child has\nsummoned us here!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.60,0:21:04.94,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Pull yourself together!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.41,0:21:09.57,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,But on that night\N17 years ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.68,0:21:13.81,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Congratulations! This is our gift\nfrom the Count!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.95,0:21:18.71,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,NO!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.69,0:21:21.78,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Madame?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.23,0:21:25.52,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.69,0:21:29.32,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Who the devil\nare you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.90,0:23:12.83,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,A poisonous evil stalks\nthe lovers.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.23,0:23:17.29,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,But I am still unaware that I am about\nto fall prey to it, as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.14,0:23:20.67,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Next time on Gankutsuou,\NThe Count of Monte Cristo, Act 9:
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.05,0:23:21.22,count fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(352,350)}Act 9:\NI Dreamed a Dark Dream
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.87,0:23:22.24,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,..."I Dreamed\na Dark Dream."
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.38,0:23:24.57,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Bide your time,\nand hold out hope!
